what was lost to friction.

00:02:38.907 --> 00:02:40.603
The other option is for the dancer

00:02:40.603 --> 00:02:44.054
to bring her arms 
or leg in closer to her body

00:02:44.054 --> 00:02:45.819
once she returns to pointe.

00:02:45.819 --> 00:02:47.040
Why does this work?

